                        <interp inst="t18440819-name-1395" type="given" value="SAMUEL"></interp>SAMUEL ALLARDICE</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a baker, and live in the Borough-market. The prisoner was in my service—it was his duty to carry bread to my cus<lb></lb>tomers, and if he received money he was to pay it to me on the same day—he has never paid me either of the sums in question, I am sure.</p>
